avings plans and investment products consisting of unit trusts individual savings accounts and open ended investment companies its gener aviva plc provides life insurance general insurance accident and health insurance and asset management products and services worldwide the company’s longterm insurance and savings products include annuities equity release products pension products such as personal and group pensions stakeholder pensions and income drawdown protection products including term assurance mortgage life insurance flexible whole of life and critical illness cover and group schemes bonds and savings comprising single premium investment bonds and regular premium savings plans and investment products consisting of unit trusts individual savings accounts and open ended investment companies its general and health insurance products comprise personal lines of insurance products such as motor household travel and creditor insurance commercial lines of insurance products including fleet liability and commercial property insurance health insurance products consisting of private health income protection and personal accident products as well as various corporate healthcare insurance products and insurance for corporate and specialty risks in addition the company offers asset management services to thirdparty investors it sells its products through a range of distribution channels including direct sales force intermediaries corporate partnerships bancassurance and joint ventures as well as through the telephone and internet the company was formerly known as cgnu plc and changed its name to aviva plc in july  aviva plc was incorporated in  and is headquartered in london united kingdom detailed description st helen’s undershaftlondon  ecp dqunited kingdomfounded in  employees phone     wwwavivacom key executives for aviva plc mr mark andrew wilson group ceo  executive director age  total annual compensation m gbp mr thomas d stoddard cfo  executive director age  total